=== 克蘇魯區 ===
{{main|克蘇魯區}}
克蘇魯區，名字源自[[霍華德·菲利普斯·洛夫克拉夫特|霍華德·菲利普斯·洛夫克拉夫特]]的作品中虛構的[[克蘇魯|神]]，是冥王星赤道上狹長、黑暗的地區，以它的形狀取的綽號是鯨魚。它的長度是{{convert|1860|mi|km|disp=flip|abbr=on}}，是冥王星上最大片的黑暗地形<ref name="whale">{{cite web|last1=Feltman|first1=Rachel|title=New map of Pluto reveals a 'whale' and a 'donut'|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2015/07/08/new-map-of-pluto-reveals-a-whale-and-a-donut/|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=8 July 2015|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401105230/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2015/07/08/new-map-of-pluto-reveals-a-whale-and-a-donut/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。推測這個區域的顏色是由被稱為複雜的碳氫化合物，該區域的暗顏色推測是由稱為[[托林_(天文學)|托林]]的焦油覆蓋的表面，這種焦油是複雜的碳氫化合物，是甲烷和大氣中的氮在紫外線和宇宙射線的交互作用下形成的<ref>{{Cite web|title = Why the Dark Spots on Pluto?|url = http://thespacewriter.com/wp/2015/07/03/why-the-dark-spots-on-pluto/|date = 3 July 2015|accessdate = 23 July 2015|last = Petersen|first = C. C.|website = TheSpacewriter's Ramblings|archive-date = 2015-07-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150723080836/http://thespacewriter.com/wp/2015/07/03/why-the-dark-spots-on-pluto/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Strange Spots on Pluto May be Tar and Frost|url = http://www.space.com/8313-strange-spots-pluto-tar-frost.html|date = 29 April 2010|accessdate = 23 July 2015|website = Space.com|last = Moskowitz|first = Clara|archive-date = 2015-07-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150721010318/http://www.space.com/8313-strange-spots-pluto-tar-frost.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Pluto's bright heart and Charon's dark spot revealed in HD {{!}} Astronomy.com|url = http://www.astronomy.com/news/2015/07/plutos-heart-revealed-as-mountainous-tombaugh-regio|date = 15 July 2015|accessdate = 23 July 2015|website = Astronomy Magazine|last = Betz|first = Eric|archive-date = 2015-07-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150723052738/http://www.astronomy.com/news/2015/07/plutos-heart-revealed-as-mountainous-tombaugh-regio|dead-url = no}}</ref>。
在克魯蘇區出現大量的隕石坑，顯示該區可能有數十億年古老，相較之下，毗鄰且相對明亮但缺乏坑洞的[[史波尼克高原|史波尼克高原]]，可能只有一億歲
<ref>{{Cite web |last=Talbert |first=Tricia |title=NASA's New Horizons Finds Second Mountain Range in Pluto's 'Heart' |url=http://www.nasa.gov/image-feature/nasa-s-new-horizons-finds-second-mountain-range-in-pluto-s-heart |date=21 July 2015 |accessdate=23 July 2015 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723013747/http://www.nasa.gov/image-feature/nasa-s-new-horizons-finds-second-mountain-range-in-pluto-s-heart/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 湯博區 ===
[[File:Tombaugh_Regio.jpg|thumb]]在2015年7月13日看見的湯博區]]
{{main|湯博區}}
湯博區，暱稱為心臟，是一大片淺色的[[心形符號|心形]]地區，以發現[[冥王星|冥王星]]的[[克萊德·湯博|克萊德·湯博]]的名字命名。心形的兩葉都有獨特的地質特徵並分享明亮的外觀，西方的葉（[[史波尼克高原|史波尼克高原]]）比東部的葉更為平滑<ref name="brokenheart">{{cite web|last1=Feltman|first1=Rachel|title=New data reveals that Pluto's heart is broken|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2015/07/14/new-data-reveals-that-plutos-heart-is-broken/|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=14 July 2015|archive-date=2017-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905000735/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2015/07/14/new-data-reveals-that-plutos-heart-is-broken/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。心的跨距大約{{convert|990|mi|km|disp=flip|abbr=on}}<ref name="whale"/>。這個區域包含  {{convert|11,000|ft|m|abbr = on|disp = flip}}高的山和冰凍的水，[[希拉蕊山|希拉蕊山]]和[[諾蓋山|諾蓋山]]在它的西南邊緣。表面缺乏撞擊坑，顯示這地區的歷史可能少於1億年，因此，冥王星可能有活躍的地質運動<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Orwig|first1 = Jessica|title = The first insanely close-up photos of Pluto reveal water on its surface|url = http://www.businessinsider.com/the-first-insanely-close-up-photos-of-pluto-reveal-water-on-its-surface-2015-7|work = Business Insider|accessdate = 15 July 2015|date = 15 July 2015|archive-date = 2016-05-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160509013704/http://www.businessinsider.com/the-first-insanely-close-up-photos-of-pluto-reveal-water-on-its-surface-2015-7|dead-url = no}}</ref>。後續的資料表明這個地區的邊緣有如冰川的冰流特徵，和有證據顯示亮的物質覆蓋在黑暗的克蘇魯區東部邊緣<ref name="NASA-20150724-lg"/>。

=== 指節套環 ===
[[File:Pluto-BrassKnuckles-20150716.jpg|thumb]] 

一系列具有半規則間隔的黑暗斑點和規則的邊界被暱稱為'''指節套環'''。它們位於赤道，界於心和鯨魚的尾巴之間，直徑平均約{{convert|300|mi|km|disp=flip|abbr=on}}<ref name="darkbelt">{{cite web|last1=Chang|first1=Kenneth|title=The Dark Belt Around Pluto|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/projects/cp/summer-of-science-2015/latest/the-dark-belt-around-pluto|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=12 July 2015|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310135259/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/projects/cp/summer-of-science-2015/latest/the-dark-belt-around-pluto|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="knuckles">{{cite web|last1=Feltman|first1=Rachel|title=Pluto shows mysterious spots in new NASA photos|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2015/07/02/pluto-shows-mysterious-spots-in-new-nasa-photos/|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=2 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715104335/http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/speaking-of-science/wp/2015/07/02/pluto-shows-mysterious-spots-in-new-nasa-photos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。從西（湯博區的南邊）到東（鯨魚的尾端），套環依序是<ref>{{cite web|last1=Chang|first1=Kenneth|title=NASA’s New Horizons Spacecraft Completes Flyby of Pluto|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/15/science/space/nasa-new-horizons-spacecraft-reaches-pluto.html|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=14 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714152023/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/15/science/space/nasa-new-horizons-spacecraft-reaches-pluto.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Rogers|first1=Adam|title=The New, Nerdy Mythology of Pluto's Place Names|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/07/new-nerdy-mythology-plutos-place-names/|work=Wired|accessdate=14 July 2015|date=14 July 2015|archive-date=2015-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118051757/http://www.wired.com/2015/07/new-nerdy-mythology-plutos-place-names|dead-url=no}}</ref>：

* [[克魯恩斑|克魯恩斑]]（Krun Macula）：以伊拉克南部[[曼德語族|曼德語族]]地獄的[[克魯恩|主神]]命名，相當於地府的[[閻羅王|閻羅王]]。
* [[阿拉斑|阿拉斑]]（Ala Macula）：以[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]東部[[依博人|依博人]]的[[阿拉|地域和收穫之神]]命名。
* [[炎魔斑|炎魔斑]]（Balrog Macula）：以[[托爾金|托爾金]]的幻想神話中的虛構的[[炎魔|惡魔人種]]命名。
* [[巫庫波卡梅斑|巫庫波卡梅斑]]（Vucub-Came Macula）和[[匈卡梅斑|匈卡梅斑]]（Hun-Came Macula）：依據[[瑪雅文明|瑪雅]][[基切人|基切語]][[波波爾·烏|議會之書]]的兩位[[瑪雅死神|死神]]命名。
* [[孟婆斑|孟婆斑]]（Meng-p'o Macula）：以[[中國佛教|中國佛教]]中讓死者忘記前世的[[孟婆|神]]命名<ref>{{Cite web |last=Wallace |first=Sam Littlefair |title=NASA gives Buddhist nickname to region of Pluto |work=Lion's Roar |url=http://www.lionsroar.com/nasa-informally-names-plutonian-region-after-buddhist-deity/ |date=15 July 2015 |accessdate=23 July 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315013410/http://www.lionsroar.com/nasa-informally-names-plutonian-region-after-buddhist-deity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

